title: Ban the name pedo
body:
Should the name pedo be added to the Denied Names list, banning it from Decentraland?

## Description

Provide a brief explanation of why this name should be banned. For example: why or to whom might it be offensive?


**[Vote on this proposal on the Decentraland DAO](https://governance.decentraland.io/en/proposal?id=11d18920-b927-11eb-aab0-c770b887e6f6)**
